entry.title: MMA CTF Writeups
entry.content:
Last weekend, the SIT competed in MMA CTF and had a few members solve challenges! If you were one of those members, we want your writeup! If you have a writeup for a challenge, please send them to Andrew and we will post them below. Thanks!

Writeups

  • Rock Paper SHELLCODE by Vincent Moscatello
  • Login as admin! by Andrew Kerr
  • Smart Cipher System, flag #4 by Robert Munyer
